# Spacing

Spacing scale + usage rules. All spacing values come from the scale.

## Scale

Based on {{4pt_/_8pt}} grid. Tokens:

| Token | Value | Typical use |
|---|---|---|
| `--space-0` | 0 | — |
| `--space-1` | {{4px}} | tight icon gaps |
| `--space-2` | {{8px}} | inline padding |
| `--space-3` | {{12px}} | {{...}} |
| `--space-4` | {{16px}} | default padding |
| `--space-6` | {{24px}} | section gap |
| `--space-8` | {{32px}} | container padding |
| `--space-12` | {{48px}} | major section break |
| `--space-16` | {{64px}} | page margins |
| {{...}} | {{...}} | {{...}} |

## Rules

- Off-grid values (e.g., 13px, 22px) forbidden
- Use semantic token classes (e.g., Tailwind `p-4`, `gap-6`) — never inline px
- Padding vs margin: prefer padding for component-internal; margin for layout composition
